  EffectDiscription_ENG: You may digivolve this card from your hand onto one of your
    blue Tamers as if the Tamer is a level 3 blue Digimon for a memory cost of 2.
    [When Digivolving] If a card with [Hybrid] in its traits or [Tommy Himi] is in
    this Digimon's digivolution cards, 1 of your opponent's Digimon with no digivolution
    cards can't attack or block until the end of their next turn.
